{"tid":2094803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"同時軍演 局勢再升溫  開真彈VS雙航母 中美南海格劍","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T06:22:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f53c0ab3604245195674576c2e1227209fce0e0","tid":2094803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:40:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200705/O5QBIGZI2L4FV77742JVQQFVTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200705%2FO5QBIGZI2L4FV77742JVQQFVTQ%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=19b40f54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200705%2FO5QBIGZI2L4FV77742JVQQFVTQ%2F&h=01b80f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200705/O5QBIGZI2L4FV77742JVQQFVTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n同時軍演 局勢再升溫 <br />\n開真彈VS雙航母 中美南海格劍<br />\n<br />\n【戰雲密佈】中國解放軍自本月1日起至5日，在南海的西沙群島一帶軍演。美軍亦公佈兩艘航母昨日由菲律賓海駛入南海，意味中美兩國同時在南海進行軍事演習，再令南海局勢升溫。美國沒有透露航母位置，但中國官方機構聲稱拍攝到美軍在菲律賓以西的黃岩島一帶，意即兩國軍演地點頗為接近。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：共機17度擾台挑釁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0M3o1tU6hSXtyLsCUWw_ESzij5M=/987x656/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NOGX7MZIYMKTMVFZ457UEFVYZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0M3o1tU6hSXtyLsCUWw_ESzij5M%3D%2F987x656%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNOGX7MZIYMKTMVFZ457UEFVYZQ.gif&h=c5038d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍六年來首次派出包括列根號（左）在內的雙航母到南海演習。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國兩大航母群列根號、尼米茲號早前已連續幾天在菲律賓海進行訓練，昨天正式前往南海繼續訓練。列根號航母群指揮官威可夫（George Wikoff）少將解釋：「軍演目的是向我們的合作夥伴和盟友明確表示，我們將致力於維持區域安全與穩定。」他透露今次軍演：「實際上比起以往短期演習所做的事項，我們這次的訓練節奏變快了，模擬的戰鬥力更高。我們進行全天候飛行訓練，每天24小時內完成數百次出擊。」美國海軍在Twitter上發佈數張相片，F/A-18「超級大黃蜂」戰機從列根號甲板起飛的照片，證實兩艘航母3日已在「菲律賓海域」演練。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_yIuzTuWnW9z0_DVhT6VjGdW104=/910x582/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FA5NFD5Z2XFLTD4JHWUKC4FLDQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_yIuzTuWnW9z0_DVhT6VjGdW104%3D%2F910x582%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFA5NFD5Z2XFLTD4JHWUKC4FLDQ.gif&h=00146e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解放軍在南海訓練實彈炮擊，模擬擊毀敵艦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美六年來首出動雙航母<br />\n<br />\n美媒《華爾街日報》形容，這是自2014年以來，美國首度在南海動用雙航母。據悉美國海軍在演習期間除了派出兩艘航母，還有四艘軍艦隨<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n意即中美雙方同時在南海軍演。<br />\n<br />\n中國解放軍1日至5日一連五天在西沙群島進行軍演。<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n在黃海海域，北部戰區054A型導彈護衞艦日照艦進行打擊海上不明目標實彈演習；在東海海域，則有052D型導彈驅逐艦廈門艦聯合開展臨檢拿捕訓練，對「可疑船隻」進行檢查拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C3v1jDPQ9At2f6JKZG2PGfchNhs=/666x574/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5KHJ2HEX6BWU6KFDT55GXF2TFU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC3v1jDPQ9At2f6JKZG2PGfchNhs%3D%2F666x574%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5KHJ2HEX6BWU6KFDT55GXF2TFU.gif&h=64ee0c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台港局勢令中共更進取<br />\n<br />\n華府智庫「美國企業研究所」（AEI）學者梅慧琳分析，隨着中國疫情控制不穩、國內民怨上升，香港政治局勢惡化，或與台灣和平統一可能性變得越來越渺茫，中國將更有動機在南海採取大膽軍事行動，增加發生衝突或戰爭的風險。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》/央廣網"},{"pid":"763117699e458ba2d58b724f6e8251e5e934a5a6","tid":2094803,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a901222e2067fde525a7088892eb1878027a41aa","tid":2094803,"uid":120913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\